score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:19:46.000Z","msg":"sor<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adbde3955aab10db2e623ef3d1fef1c76ea0fce","tid":1631614,"uid":160650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:20:19.000Z","msg":"好多滲透 保持清醒 唔好被仇恨支配"},{"pid":"93763d8bf519b697b857b00bb41d1a49e502ac8d","tid":1631614,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4165086d3fcedf90ac936d7cda5e9579061a7a","tid":1631614,"uid":160650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:21:43.000Z","msg":"巴打 努力推上去，等多啲人見到<br />\n<br />\n大家唔係想屌前線！！"},{"pid":"10592db8f99caeac8ba4e1533e1094f6d412ef76","tid":1631614,"uid":160650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:01.000Z","msg":"努力再推"},{"pid":"ca69d2d3cdcbbf0bd56c5160f4d10cc920160164","tid":1631614,"uid":160650,"like":0