又唔解釋任何理由既極危險"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"呢個post應該佢地試水溫<br />\n<br />\n大大話話我之前block落有三四十個喺入面出現返再互屌<br />\n<br />\n今次成功之後實好撚多類似嘅post"},{"pid":"3ce6e512c4ec4f3a9844e63afd9d22b4e3f8d9b8","tid":1631614,"uid":270576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"國際輿論開始轉風向：<br />\n<br />\nBBC:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=11950049\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&h=20132a5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548</a><br />\nAnti-government marches in Hong Kong have ended in rioting, with attacks on government offices, a metro station and businesses with ties to mainland China.<br />\n<br />\nCNN:<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=a16f06fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=53844d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html</a><br />\nViolent protests which began Friday stretched into the early hours of Saturday, beyond the midnight deadline when the new anti-mask regulations began. They spread out across the city and soon devolved into violent clashes, with protesters throwing petrol bombs and police responding with pepper spray and tear gas.<br />\n<br />\nUN rights chief :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2Fun-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence%2F&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=f86aaf2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/</a><br />\nUN human rights chief Michelle Bachelet said Saturday she was &ldquo;troubled&rdquo; by Hong Kong&rsquo;s increasingly violent pro-democracy protests<br />\n<br />\n開始無人話警察武力不對等，國際開始支持港府。再係咁落去，美國人權及民主法案好可能被否決<br />\n<br />\n中國共產黨唔係咁易對付，一定要用智慧去推翻共匪政權。所以，希望可以堅持以下五點：<br />\n<br />\n一、重組前線<br />\n其實又要前線行動又要佢地用腦係好辛苦，加上好多前線十分年輕，社會經驗不足，亦無咩歷史智慧。因此，我建議禁止中學或以下學生參與前線行動，以免佢地一時情緒影響大局。另外，如果發現有前線情緒或智力有問題，都要即刻阻止佢繼續上前線。如此安排參考咗二戰時期耐久戰對有PTSD軍人既處理方法。<br />\n<br />\n二、建立紀律部隊，阻止極端暴力行為<br />\n其實無一場革命可以由烏合之眾組成而成功，所以我地要建立紀律部隊，有一個清晰目標先行動，而唔係盲從「前線決定」。所有行動都要遵守正義之戰(just war theory)原則，一定要合符比例、有必要的。睇返阿拉伯之春，內戰既國家最後都好難建立民主。我相信，如果要用真係反抗，唔可以再用呢家誰大誰惡誰正確既方法。<br />\n<br />\n三、停止無差別攻擊，對準政權<br />\n所有革命都一定要有一個特定既敵人先會贏，因為咁先可以得到更多資汛，引誘更多人背叛政權。所以，民用裝修一律停止。只可增加政權成本。<br />\n<br />\n四、不再高舉「前線決定」，收歸文宣<br />\n正如前述，前線智慧不比一般人高，不必神化，反而佢地既一個錯誤要所有人承擔，所以要將武官系統重新回歸民官系統，安排於文宣部之下，先有文宣目標，後有行動。<br />\n<br />\n五、和理非不是condom，無必要次次幫低智前線執屎<br />\n2014年左膠主導左79日，勇武2019年主導遠超79日，但現在勢頭下降，應知所進退，把策略部分交由政治精英處理。"}]}